Canada                    4.9%        2.5%        30.1%      19.3%
EU                       17.3%       11.1%       162.4%     104.0%
Japan                    14.2%        9.0%       589.0%     500.7%
US                        9.5%        6.5%       536.9%     429.5%
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
