16.3m); earnings fell to 2.9p (3.1p) per share.
The pre-tax outcome for the half year showed a 25 per cent advance to Pounds
3.27m (Pounds 2.61m). Turnover for the period totalled Pounds 36.8m (Pounds
30.9m). Earnings emerged at 4.8p (4.5p). There is no interim dividend this
time against 0.75p in 1993.
